OL,3,CWales at Six: Should Wales introduce a
OL,4,Ctourism tax for visitors?
OL,6,FShould holdaymakers in Wales be
OL,7,Fcharged when they come to stay
OL,8,Fovernight?
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government think so, and the
OL,11,FSenedd has voted to take plans to
OL,12,Fintroduce a tourism tax a step closer
OL,13,Fto reality.
OL,15,FThe Visitor Levy would mean anyone
OL,16,Fholidaying in Wales would have to pay
OL,17,Fa fee per person per night that would
OL,18,Fbe re-invested into local communities.
