OL,3,CWales at Six: Should Wales introduce a
OL,4,Ctourism tax for visitors?
OL,6,FSupporters of the idea say a small
OL,7,Fcharge would help to pay for ameneties
OL,8,Fin tourist hotspots, while critics
OL,9,Fclaim it'll drive people away.
OL,11,FA Wales at Six special hears from
OL,12,Fthose on both sides of the argument
OL,13,Facross Wales, assessing what it all
OL,14,Fmeans for communities, businesses and
OL,15,Fholidaymakers, while we also travel to
OL,16,FIbiza to see whether a similar policy
OL,17,Fhas helped or hindered the Spanish
OL,18,FIsland.
